  {
    
    "name": "Section 1",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-612221215116887003 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/korean-skincare-uk/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=612221215066555355&sectionId=612221215116887003)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_dayLabel","label":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_dayLabel","default":"Days"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_hourLabel","label":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_hourLabel","default":"Hours"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_minuteLabel","label":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_minuteLabel","default":"Minutes"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_secondLabel","label":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_secondLabel","default":"Seconds"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_weekLabel","label":"ggnKJV-_c3Y_weekLabel","default":"Weeks"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-y_CqzXB6_text","label":"gg-y_CqzXB6_text","default":"<p>Join us on <strong>Wednesday, April 15, from 17:00 to 20:00</strong> BST for the 6th edition of the Hunt.&nbsp;</p><p>By participating in this exclusive online event, you can save up to <strong>50% OFF</strong> by hunting limited-use discount codes all over our website. Prove your eye for detail and look for the iconic items to catch the highest discount!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwAblpBw6U_label","label":"ggwAblpBw6U_label","default":"<p>Get your cart ready</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0d_eP77C1_childItem_0","label":"gg0d_eP77C1_childItem_0","default":"<p>\"Is there some reason that my coffee isn&#039;t here? Has she died or something?\"&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUmmImfIj9_text","label":"ggUmmImfIj9_text","default":"<p>You’ve just been selected as Miranda Priestly’s new assistant at the prestigious Gloway Magazine, and your very first challenge has already been assigned.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The office is buzzing, phones ringing, emails pinging. A million girls would kill for this job, but surviving it takes more than ambition; you need a <strong>booster </strong>to keep you moving. <strong>Caffeine </strong>will be your friend in this endeavor.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Here, details are everything. And “on time”? That’s already late. When a meeting is set for <strong>3:45</strong>, there’s no room for a <strong>glacial </strong>pace, Miranda expects her <strong>coffee </strong>ready before it even begins.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Prove what you’re capable of. This role demands speed and sharp <strong>multi</strong>tasking, along with the ability to track down even the hardest-to-find items. And precision matters above all: don't go confusing <strong>truffle </strong>brown with <strong>caramel</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>We can’t wait to see your skills in action. And remember: Miranda expects nothing less than flawless delivery.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHjyOAxlLq_childItem_0","label":"ggHjyOAxlLq_childItem_0","default":"<p>\"By all means, move at a glacial pace. You know how that thrills me.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6ZCWs0QDe_text","label":"gg6ZCWs0QDe_text","default":"<p>STEP 1</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9diQUVKNp_text","label":"gg9diQUVKNp_text","default":"<p><strong>Fill your shopping cart</strong> or wish list before the Hunt, so you are <strong>ready </strong>to check out when you find a code.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXgo9oM9_W_text","label":"ggXgo9oM9_W_text","default":"<p>STEP 2</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOfgLUyQh3_text","label":"ggOfgLUyQh3_text","default":"<p>Hunt down the specific items and their <strong>codes hidden everywhere</strong> on our website when the Hunt starts!&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdN84dMe5u_text","label":"ggdN84dMe5u_text","default":"<p>STEP 3</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRKkQMby9T_text","label":"ggRKkQMby9T_text","default":"<p>Found a code? Hurry and <strong>use it at checkout</strong> before someone else does!&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpVVQUHOSJ_text","label":"ggpVVQUHOSJ_text","default":"<p>EXTRA</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpqqAoA0Uj_text","label":"ggpqqAoA0Uj_text","default":"<p>Open your order to find out if you're the lucky winner of the Golden Envelope <strong>worth £85</strong>!*</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggo8v8X7krk_label","label":"ggo8v8X7krk_label","default":"<p>Prepare you cart</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDNmwxrHo1_text","label":"ggDNmwxrHo1_text","default":"<p><strong>Quick tips:</strong><br>1. Use your desktop, it will make hunting much easier.<br>2. Follow us on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/koreanskincare_official/\"><strong><u>Instagram</u></strong></a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KoreanSkincare.official\"><strong><u>Facebook</u></strong></a> to get all the updates, tips &amp; hints before and during the Hunt.</p><p>3. Some clues are already hidden on this page, with more coming to our social media in the next few weeks, so stay tuned!</p><p>*A Golden Envelope containing a £85 gift card will be hidden in one lucky order placed during the Hunt.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMT22uqDx9_childItem_0","label":"ggMT22uqDx9_childItem_0","default":"<p>\"Don&#039;t be ridiculous, Andrea, everybody wants a discount… \"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzkfAvZgJM_text","label":"ggzkfAvZgJM_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 60 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIrJtyPlNF_text","label":"ggIrJtyPlNF_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 50 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggN9kLGR5jS_text","label":"ggN9kLGR5jS_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 40 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkBPQA0_hH_text","label":"ggkBPQA0_hH_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 60 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWYNyhY12D_text","label":"ggWYNyhY12D_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 50 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwbnyZEHy6_text","label":"ggwbnyZEHy6_text","default":"<p><strong>10 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 40 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggScYQv25pB_text","label":"ggScYQv25pB_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 20 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggimYSQsaBE_text","label":"ggimYSQsaBE_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 20 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7xsvkRBF7_text","label":"gg7xsvkRBF7_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 6 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggu9D_GYdpz_text","label":"ggu9D_GYdpz_text","default":"<p><strong>3 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable once, released hourly during the Hunt*</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8WRlNJuiW_text","label":"gg8WRlNJuiW_text","default":"<p><strong>5 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable 6 times</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglrTOEMZBO_text","label":"gglrTOEMZBO_text","default":"<p><strong>3 different codes</strong></p><p>Each usable once, released hourly during the Hunt*</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMBsmrSOBt_text","label":"ggMBsmrSOBt_text","default":"<p><strong>Important notes for your quest:</strong></p><p>1. Codes can be used a limited amount of times. If the code you have found doesn’t work, it means it has already been used the maximum amount of times. Don’t get discouraged and keep hunting!<br>2. Codes can’t be combined with other discount codes.<br>3. Read the <a href=\"#g65VF7uyqW\"><u>Terms &amp; Conditions</u></a>.</p><p>*The 50% codes will be hidden at 3 different times: 17:00 BST, 18:00 BST, and 19:00 BST.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9AquLAnZn_childItem_0","label":"gg9AquLAnZn_childItem_0","default":"<p>\"The devil is in the details...\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggz7qPG4-6Z_text","label":"ggz7qPG4-6Z_text","default":"<p>Here are some examples of what the hidden codes could look like during the Hunt:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggkcB4kqFBF_childItem_0","label":"ggkcB4kqFBF_childItem_0","default":"<p>\"Please, bore someone else with your questions.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_0","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_0","default":"<p>How do I participate in the Hunt?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_1","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_1","default":"<p>When does the Hunt start?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_2","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_2","default":"<p>Can I hunt on the KS App?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_3","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_3","default":"<p>Where will the discount codes be hidden?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_4","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_4","default":"<p>How do I know if I’ve found a valid code?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_5","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_5","default":"<p>Can I save my discount code for another time?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_6","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_6","default":"<p>Are the discount codes the same for everyone?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_7","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_7","default":"<p>What kind of discounts can I find?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_8","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_8","default":"<p>Can I order everything I want with the discount codes?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_9","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_9","default":"<p>Will the Hunt be available on all your websites?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_10","label":"ggxe1I9-Ewi_childItem_10","default":"<p>Will I receive KS Points with my order?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg52snXMYd9_text","label":"gg52snXMYd9_text","default":"<p>Simply visit our website during the event and start searching for hidden items with discount codes before someone else uses them. We recommend using the desktop version to make sure you don't miss anything. It's also advised to prepare your order and be registered before the Hunt starts, so you can use your discount code as quickly as possible!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmoKBrpEjP_text","label":"ggmoKBrpEjP_text","default":"<p>Date: Wednesday, April 15, 2026.<br>Time: 17:00 – 20:00 BST.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglPtvsAUkx_text","label":"gglPtvsAUkx_text","default":"<p>Yes, the Hunt is available on the app, but hunting on your desktop will be easier.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEsv4dAgJe_text","label":"ggEsv4dAgJe_text","default":"<p>Codes will be scattered across different pages of our website. Keep an eye on banners, product pictures, product descriptions, and even blog posts! Some clues are already hidden on this page, with more coming to our social media in the next few weeks, so stay tuned!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjyd24BNc__text","label":"ggjyd24BNc__text","default":"<p>Try applying it at checkout and make sure to use it within the time of the event. If the code works, you’re in luck. If it doesn’t, it may have expired or reached its usage limit.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfldlEt2d4_text","label":"ggfldlEt2d4_text","default":"<p>No, you must use your code before the event ends at 20:00 BST. After that, it will no longer be valid. Be fast, the codes have a limited number of uses, so others might claim them first!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4fN2z9TMC_text","label":"gg4fN2z9TMC_text","default":"<p>Yes, everyone will see the same codes, but act fast: it’s first-come, first-served!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggarI47kx87_text","label":"ggarI47kx87_text","default":"<p>Discounts vary! You may find 10%, 15%, 20%, 25%, 30%, or even 50% OFF discount codes!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIAPbEF7i4_text","label":"ggIAPbEF7i4_text","default":"<p>You can treat yourself, but note the maximum order value is €500 before the code is applied, and gift cards are excluded.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeHhXQEMuj_text","label":"ggeHhXQEMuj_text","default":"<p>The Hunt is only available on:<br>koreanskincare.com<br>koreanskincare.nl<br>korean-skincare.de<br>koreanskincare.co.uk<br>korean-skincare.fr</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggfF0Ytus9t_text","label":"ggfF0Ytus9t_text","default":"<p>Yes, you will receive KS Points on the website you order from.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_zZFLPOSR_label","label":"gg_zZFLPOSR_label","default":"<p>Read the Terms &amp; Conditions</p>"}],
